text: This Company needs to control its drivers better the residents I live in is a 20 mile an hour speed limit. One of their drivers trying to make a good tip was driving 40 miles an hour down narrow roads in our community. If you value your lives or your friends lives don’t call these people to come to your home

text: Ordered 4 pizzas. Never order mushrooms.. there was mushrooms on one. They said wait 15-20 mins for another. But the other three would be cold and I had to bring the pizzas for a B-Day party so I couldn't wait.
